---
title: "Section 5 - Model EXEC Folder"
output: html_document
---


The EXEC folder contains the following executables used by the CT-RAMP model:

*	arc_all.jar - the ARC CT-RAMP Java archive file containing all the Java code.

*	filesToKeep.bat - the DOS batch file used for archiving files. It reads fileToKeep.txt for a list of files to keep.
